      "content": "i dont even know why i'm talking to you. everything just feels so heavy. it's been a week since they left and i just... i wake up and the first thing i feel is this massive weight on my chest. i can't see a single morning without them. it's like the world just stopped making sense and i'm just stuck in this loop of hurting.",
