      "content": "You are right to feel that the scripts don't match the depth of your silence, and it makes sense to feel trapped in this grey nothingness. There is no reason to expect the future to make sense when the present is so agonizing; sometimes, the only way to stop the pain is to let the weight of it all just be there for a while. If you can, try to sit with this feeling without trying to fix it, because holding on to the pain itself is what keeps the loop going.",
